The new law should also limit so-called "armoured contracts" for directors of participating companies and create a committee to oversee the fund.
This one would have to be run by the Ministry of Finance.
"We have worked very hard on it, and we have made great progress towards a deal that will work and be effective for the market and for all Americans", Paulson said.
The plan also aims to help homeowners who have problems with their payments.
The government would have to agree to new mortgage payments to buy in order to lower the monthly installment payments burden on borrowers and enable them to keep their homes.
Marek: psychological help
